usage: Kellogg's Pop-Tarts Frosted Cookies & Creme Toaster Pastries. See side for details. Naturally & artificially flavored. 8 toaster pastries. Directions Fully baked & ready to eat! Or enjoy them toasty warm!Remove from pouch before heating.For toaster:1. Warm pastry in toaster at lowest heat setting.2. Cool briefly before handling.For microwave:1. Place pastry on microwave safe plate.2. Heat on high for 3 seconds.3. Cool briefly before handling.Caution: if pastry is overheated, frosting/filling can become extremely hot and could cause burns. Due to possible risk of fire, never leave appliance unattended while in use. Children should be supervised. Appliances vary. Be sure your appliance is clean and functioning correctly. Times given are approximate. Warnings Contains wheat, milk, egg and soy ingredients.
